'''Phantom Ray''' is an {{Rarity|Uncommon}} fish found in the [[Desolate Deep]].

== Description ==
{{Description|The Phantom Ray is a menacing yet beautiful species of ray, resembling the shape of an anchor with bioluminescent engravings throughout its body, as well as a translucent fin that they use to move around. They typically like to feed on microorganisms during the night, and spend most of the day sitting underneath ledges or large vegetation.|Bestiary Entry}}

